    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"letting the noise stop\"... that's the only thing that sounds peaceful. Most people talk about \"fighting\" or \"getting through it,\" but that just sounds like more noise. Like I'm being told to keep struggling just to maintain a status quo that doesn't even matter. You're saying it doesn't have to be a big thing? Like, just... stepping aside?",
